         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility"> ¶ Hamburg, ¶  ¶ 30 January 1857 ¶ Most esteemed ¶  ¶ Professor, ¶  ¶  ¶ There is now a ship loading ¶  ¶ for Sydney, which is due to leave in mid-February. I am despatching a small box by it to Dr Mu...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">M57.01.30</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Wilhelm Sonder to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Diederich von Schlechtendal</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">MS not seen; text given here extracted from Tkach, Neubauer &amp; Roser (2022), Brief</seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">30.</seg>
                  </p>
                  <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
               </note>Hamburg d. 30 Jan.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>57</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Geehrtester Herr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Professor!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es liegt jetzt ein Schiff in Landung nach Sidney, das Mitte Februar abgehen soll. Ich befördere damit eine kleine Kiste an Dr. Müller und möchte Sie bitten, wenn es Ihnen möglich ist, mir die Abdrucke von den letzten Beiträgen zu den Plant. Müller., die ich im Septemberheft von 1856 gesehen habe, bis dahin zuzusenden. Sie werden auch Hooker’s Journal gesehen haben, dass Dr. Müller in diesem Frühjahr nach Sidney zurückkehren wird; ich möchte nun gerne, dass er dort alles bekäme, was bis jetzt über seine Pflanzen gedruckt ist.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Ich kann Ihnen nächstens wieder, wenn Sie wünschen, einiges Manuskript senden.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Ihr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>hochachtungsvoll ergebener</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hamburg,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>30 January 1857</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Most esteemed<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Professor,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>There is now a ship loading<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for Sydney, which is due to leave in mid-February. I am despatching a small box by it to Dr Mueller and would like to ask you if it is possible for you to send me<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>by then<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the reprints of the last contributions to the Plantae Muellerianae which I saw in the September issue of 1856. You will also have seen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Hooker's Journal that Dr Mueller will be returning to Sydney this spring; I would now like him to have there all that has so far been printed about his plants.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I can send you some manuscript again soon, if you wish.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>respectfully devoted</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
